TestDiscoverFindsTestGoals
/ Calls test.discover against a fixture directory with three built
/ *.fixture.goal files. Asserts the discover result has length 3. The outer
/ runner uses pattern '*.test.goal' so it ignores these fixtures.
- test.discover tests in '_fixtures' recursive, pattern='*.fixture.goal', write to %tests%
- list.count %tests%, write to %count%
- assert %count% equals 3
